 />\n毒坤就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d8efdddc3920d090e81ce1e2582d7fa1f86efa","tid":46361,"uid":45218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:20:50.000Z","msg":"肥欣宜係樣衰加肥 但唱歌都唔錯 聽佢同胃腩一齊唱陰天假期 真係俾佢驚艷到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得佢嗰次唱live完佳將胃腩比下去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人覺得 如果佢講少啲佢老母同埋唔好成日話咩「i wanna be myself 」呢啲廢話 認認真真唱歌 做音樂 低調啲嘅話 連登仔應該會對佢改觀好多 睇下林二汶未減肥之前都好多高登仔捧佢啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相反呢隻偽毒 冇實力之餘成日溝女仲要扮毒撚 真係頂唔撚緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我對肥欣宜可以係話冇好感 但對偽毒真係好撚憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250cb468a7e50622cd7bae11baaa829842c8cde2","tid":46361,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:23:30.000Z","msg":"上面張圖 欣宜後面2個肥婆笑得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牙醫rip"},{"pid":"2c769bfda8b30e9c5eacd0f90e3190853fd4c0fa","tid":46361,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面張圖 欣宜後面2個肥婆笑得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牙醫rip</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗佢副骨都就頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6e8802a77a05f9857262c00b74301f947bb4c6","tid":46361,"uid":36481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:26:03.000Z","msg":"狗公坤正一廢人<br />\n淨係靠炒作<br />\n今年明明極廢<br />\n又借消費sita同埋健吾哩個朋黨寫衰陳柏宇黎上位<br />\n食屎啦，狗公坤！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/